WEBVTT

00:00:00.621 --> 00:00:04.292
As a doctor in the field
of pain management,

00:00:04.333 --> 00:00:08.046
I work in a world
where you bring us your pain

00:00:08.087 --> 00:00:09.338
and we treat it.

00:00:10.089 --> 00:00:11.549
We ask questions,

00:00:11.549 --> 00:00:13.968
we take the symptoms you present,

00:00:14.010 --> 00:00:15.845
we decide what tests to run.

00:00:16.304 --> 00:00:19.640
We listen with compassion and wisdom

00:00:19.640 --> 00:00:22.018
and choose the best course of action

00:00:22.060 --> 00:00:25.980
based on our knowledge and experience
combined with science.

00:00:26.439 --> 00:00:29.484
And sometimes in a very
small window of time.